      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on. While it shows some light, honest wear from being enjoyed, it remains very clean and presents beautifully both inside and out. It\u2019s a wonderful choice for anyone looking for a dependable and stylish car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
