    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is sound and drives smoothly, with all major systems functioning as they should. The interior is clean and shows only light signs of use, while the exterior remains attractive despite some minor rock chips and very light surface scratches consistent with careful driving. It is a dependable, high-quality car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
