    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine runs steadily, but there is a minor oil seep and the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft, suggesting that some bushings may need replacement soon. The exterior has several noticeable door dings and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind performing some ongoing maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical reliability and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a sophisticated driving experience and enduring performance. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to quality and rigorous upkeep. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the exceptional value and refined character of this professional selection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
