    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and comfort, having been kept in impressive overall condition by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a deep, mirror-like shine, with only minor cosmetic imperfections such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a tiny scuff on the rear passenger door that are barely noticeable. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and free of any odors; the leather upholstery remains soft and intact, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014it starts promptly, accelerates smoothly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has been serviced regularly, and the tires have significant tread remaining. This is a well-maintained, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
